cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper involves analyzing human motion for humanoids with the objective of developing methods for autonomous multi-contact motion planning. This falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves analyzing motion capture data, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV) or machine learning (cs.LG). The objective of developing methods for autonomous motion planning could also fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves analyzing transitions and poses, which could fall under computer graphics (cs.GR).
